Package com.mygdx.hanto.implementation.common

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HantoPiece
    This inferface is used to specify a piece and a hex on the board where the piece will be placed.
    PieceMoveStrategy
    This interface specifies the specific moving strategy behaviors for different hanto pieces.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Coordinate
    Implementation of HantoCoordinate that is used in the concrete HantoGame implementations.
    HantoBoard
    This is the board for all the the Hanto Game.
    HantoGameImpl
    This is the implementation of any Internal Hanto Game.
    HantoRuleSet
    This is the rule set for all the hanto games.
    HantoState
    This abstract class describes the state of the Hanto Game and all the state classes of the specific hanto game should extend this class.
